nato-description = A coalition of European countries and its allies including the United States, the United Kingdom
                France, Germany, and Italy, to name a few; united against the still present threat of the Warsaw pact, which
                managed to stay together through the collapse of the soviet union, and its ever growing stock of future weapons.

pact-description = Despite the collapse of the soviet union, the arms and space races with america continued as the new federation
                was still nostalgic to the old regime, yet embraced democracy and rapidly conquered its former
                territories such as Poland and the baltics, although Ukraine was spared under threat of NATO intervention.

usmc-description = The United States Marine Corps, they have a proud history from island hopping, to Vietnam, to the sandbox in the middle east, to the shores of Europe, they have seen it all.

vdv-description = The russian airborne forces, or VDV for short, are an elite Russian air assault division.

